                "He does such an amazing job explaining how all the intricate details about SEO actually work and he gets the best results I've seen in the industry hands down."
              </p>
              <div class="pt-4 border-t border-neutral-200 flex items-center justify-between">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <div class="h-8 w-8 rounded-full bg-purple-100 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold text-purple-600">AA</div>
                  <div>
                    <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-900">Angelo A.</div>
                    <div class="text-xs text-neutral-500">Agency Owner</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-1">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="text-amber-400">
