                "He has completely transformed my website, ensuring it connects with the right audience through amazing SEO and seamless automation."
              </p>
              <div class="pt-4 border-t border-neutral-200 flex items-center justify-between">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <div class="h-8 w-8 rounded-full bg-purple-100 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold text-purple-600">HJ</div>
                  <div>
                    <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-900">Heather J.</div>
                    <div class="text-xs text-neutral-500">Holistic Practitioner</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-1">
